defaultLocale.name: In My Pocket
defaultLocale.description: For all those who are missing the old Firefox Pocket addon, here is an unofficial client for the excellent Pocket service. Goal is to provide a useful, but still lightweight means to access your Pocket account from your browser. Enjoy!
